name: snmp fetch values --> build SQL query --> update db
delete and rebuild empty db table every time flow starts
periodically fetch device object values and update db
then optionally load records from snmp object list
info:
if this step is skipped, points will be named on the XML Web Service as devicename_oid instead of devicename_objectname
eg "DGS-12010-52MP_sysUpTime" or "DGS-12010-52MP_1.3.6.1.2.1.1.3.0"

template:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<root>
    <header/>
    <body>
        <queryparams>
        </queryparams>
        <objects>
            {{#payload}}
            {{#objectname}}
            <{{devicename}}_{{objectname}} id="{{id}}" deviceName="{{devicename}}" objectName="{{objectname}}" oid="{{oid}}" tstr="{{tstr}}" updated="{{updated}}">
                {{value}}
            </{{devicename}}_{{objectname}}>
            {{/objectname}}
            {{^objectname}}
            <{{devicename}}_{{oid}} id="{{id}}" deviceName="{{devicename}}" objectName="{{objectname}}" oid="{{oid}}" tstr="{{tstr}}" updated="{{updated}}">
                {{value}}
            </{{devicename}}_{{oid}}>
            {{/objectname}}
            {{/payload}}
        </objects>
    </body>
</root>
